manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Is it a first aid kit? Or a survival kit? How about both.

COMPREHENSIVE FIRST AID With a Velcro tear-away Molle backer, First Aid Plus was designed to easily strap on adventure vehicles of all kinds—taking peace of mind to the trails. The First Aid Plus' MOLLE system allows for attachment to your car, boat, UTV or backpack. Quickly detach the kit with its removable velcro back panel. EMERGENCY TOOLS + GEAR REPAIR Supplies fit securely into labeled pockets, organized by injury and use case. In addition to first aid supplies, this kit also includes essential survival equipment like a multi-tool, matches, flashlight, and more. From our flashlight to multi-tool to matches to duct tape and more, it’s the First Aid kit that wants to be a Survival kit. And maybe it is. ELEMENT PROOF CASE Waterproof construction and an airtight, durable tarpaulin shell keep your supplies protected from the elements. Crossing the lines between a first aid kit and a survival gear pouch, the First Aid Plus is the perfect kit for your home, car, boat, or backpack.

About Us Founded in Nov 2016, Park City UT’s Uncharted Supply Co’s mission is to provide high-quality, intuitive gear to help people navigate emergencies big and small. From their appearance on Shark Tank, to placements in the Museum of Modern Art, to the product selected for use by government and private security agencies around the world, Uncharted has continued to design products that have saved lives around the world. Built for adventure. Waterproof contruction and an airtight, durable tarpaulin shell keep your supplies protected from the elements.
